\c 7
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli bangabantu abangcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni
\p
\v 1 Lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho isikungenisa elizweni oya kulo ukudla ilifa lalo, ixotshe izizwe ezinengi phambi kwakho\x + 31.3. Hlab. 44.2,3.\x*, amaHethi lamaGirigashi lamaAmori lamaKhanani lamaPerizi lamaHivi lamaJebusi\x + Eks. 13.5.\x*, izizwe eziyisikhombisa ezinkulu lezilamandla kulawe\x + 4.38. 9.1. 11.23.\x*,
\v 2 lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izinikela phambi kwakho\x + 7.23. Dute. 23.14.\x*, uzazitshaya, uzitshabalalise lokuzitshabalilisa\x + Eks. 22.20. Levi 27.28,29. Nani 21.2,3. Dute. 2.34. 3.6. 13.15. 20.17. Josh. 6.17,21; 8.26. 10.1,37,39. 11.11,12,21.\x*. Ungenzi isivumelwano lazo, ungabi lasihawu kuzo\x + Eks. 23.32. Dute.20.10. Josh. 2.14. 9.18. Hlu. 1.24.\x*.
\v 3 Ungathathani lazo, unganiki indodakazi yakho kundodana yakhe, njalo indodakazi yakhe ungayithatheli indodana yakho\x + Josh. 23.12. Eks. 34.16.\x*.
\v 4 Ngoba izaphambula indodana yakho ekungilandeleni, ukuze bakhonze abanye onkulunkulu; ngakho ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* luzalivuthela, lukubhubhise masinyane\x + 6.15.\x*.
\v 5 Kodwa-ke lizakwenza njalo kuzo; lizadiliza amalathi azo\x + Eks. 34.13.\x*, liphahlaze insika zazo eziyizithombe\x + Eks. 34.13.\x*, ligamule izixuku zabo, litshise ngomlilo izithombe zazo ezibaziweyo.
\v 6 Ngoba uyisizwe esingcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Eks. 19.6. Dute. 14.2. 26.19. 28.9. Jer. 2.3.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikukhethile ukuthi ube yisizwe sayo kanye, kuzo zonke izizwe ezisebusweni bomhlaba\x + Eks. 19.5.3.2. 1 Pet. 2.9.\x*.
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* kayehliselanga uthando lwayo phezu kwenu, kumbe ilikhethe, ngenxa yokuthi lalibanengi kulaziphi izizwe; ngoba lalibalutshwana kulazo zonke izizwe\x + 10.22.\x*;
\v 8 kodwa kungenxa yokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yalithanda\x + 10.15. Hos. 11.1. Mal. 1.2. Dute. 33.3.\x*, langenxa yokuthi yayizagcina isifungo eyasifunga kuboyihlo\x + Eks. 32.13. Hlab. 105.9-11.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* yalikhupha ngesandla esilamandla, yakuhlenga endlini yobugqili, esandleni sikaFaro inkosi yeGibhithe\x + 4.34.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho yazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho inguNkulunkulu, uNkulunkulu othembekileyo\x + Isa. 49.7. 1 Kor. 1.9. 10.13. 2 Kor. 1.18. 1 Joha. 1.9. 1 Thes. 5.24. 2 Thes. 3.3. 2 Tim. 2.13. Heb. 11.11.\x*, ogcina isivumelwano lomusa kubo abamthandayo labagcina imilayo yakhe, kuze kube sezizukulwaneni eziyinkulungwane\x + Eks. 20.6. Dute. 5.10. Neh. 1.5. 9.32. Dan. 9.4.\x*,
\v 10 lophindisela abamzondayo ebusweni babo, ukubabhubhisa\x + Isa. 59.18. Nah. 1.2.\x*. Kayikuphuza komzondayo, uzamphindisela ebusweni bakhe\x + 32.35.\x*.
\v 11 Ngakho uzagcina imilayo lezimiso lezahlulelo engikulaya zona lamuhla ukuzenza.
\s Izibusiso zokulalela
\p
\v 12 Kuzakuthi ngoba lisizwa lezizahlulelo, lizigcine, lizenze\x + Levi 26.3. Dute. 28.1-14.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakugcinela isivumelwano lomusa eyakufungela oyihlo\x + Hlab. 105.8. Luka 1.55,72,73.\x*.
\v 13 Njalo izakuthanda, ikubusise, ikwandise\x + Joha. 14.21.\x*. Futhi izabusisa isithelo sesizalo sakho, lesithelo selizwe lakho, amabele akho, lewayini lakho elitsha, lamafutha akho, umqegu wenkomo zakho, lemihlambi yezimvu zakho, elizweni alifungela oyihlo ukukunika lona\x + 28.4.\x*.
\v 14 Uzabusiswa kulazo zonke izizwe; kakuyikuba khona phakathi kwakho owesilisa ongazaliyo lowesifazana oyinyumba, loba phakathi kwezifuyo zakho\x + Eks. 23.26.\x*.
\v 15 LeN\nd kosi\nd* izasusa kuwe wonke umkhuhlane; kayiyikukwehlisela lasinye sezifo ezimbi zeGibhithe ozaziyo, kodwa izazehlisela phezu kwabo bonke abakuzondayo\x + 28.60. Eks. 9.14. 15.26. Dute. 28.27.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo uzabaqothula bonke abantu ezabanikela kuwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 7.2.\x*; ilihlo lakho lingabazweli, ungakhonzi onkulunkulu babo\x + 13.8; 19.13,21; 25.12.\x*, ngoba lokhu kuzakuba ngumjibila kuwe\x + 7.25. Hlu. 8.27. Eks. 23.33.\x*.
\v 17 Nxa uzakuthi enhliziyweni yakho: Izizwe lezi zinengi kulami; ngingazixotsha njani elifeni lazo\x + Nani 33.53. Eks. 15.9.\x*?
\v 18 Ungazesabi\x + 1.29. 31.6.\x*, khumbula kuhle lokho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho eyakwenza kuFaro lakuGibhithe lonke\x + Hlab. 77.11. 105.5.\x*,
\v 19 izilingo ezinkulu ilihlo lakho elazibonayo, lezibonakaliso, lezimangaliso, lesandla esilamandla, lengalo eyeluliweyo, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho eyakukhupha ngakho. IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakwenza njalo kuzo zonke izizwe ozesabayo\x + 4.34.\x*.
\v 20 Futhi-ke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izathumela olonyovu phakathi kwazo, zize zibhujiswe eziseleyo lezicatshele ubuso bakho\x + Eks.23.28. Josh. 24.12.\x*.
\v 21 Kaliyikutshaywa luvalo ngazo\x + 1.29. 31.6.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho iphakathi kwakho\x + Nani 11.20. 14.14,42. Josh. 3.10.\x*, uNkulunkulu omkhulu lowesabekayo\x + 10.17. Neh. 1.5. 4.14. 9.32.\x*.
\v 22 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izazingcothula lezizizwe phambi kwakho kancinyane kancinyane; ungeziqede masinyane, hlezi izilo zeganga zikwandele\x + Eks. 23.29,30.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izazinikela phambi kwakho, iziphazamise ngokuphazamiseka okukhulu, zize zichithwe.
\v 24 Izanikela ezandleni zakho amakhosi azo\x + Josh. 10.24,25,42. 12.1.\x*, njalo uzacitsha ibizo lawo lisuke ngaphansi kwamazulu\x + Eks. 17.14. Dute. 9.14. 25.19. 29.20.\x*; kakulamuntu ozakuma phambi kwakho uze uzibhubhise\x + 11.25. Josh. 1.5. Josh. 10.8. 23.9.\x*.
\v 25 Izithombe ezibaziweyo zabonkulunkulu bazo lizazitshisa ngomlilo\x + 7.5.12.3. Eks. 32.20. 1 Lan. 14.12.\x*. Ungafisi isiliva legolide elikuzo, ungazithatheli lona\x + Josh. 7.1,21.\x*, hlezi ubanjwe emjibileni ngalo\x + 7.16.\x*, ngoba liyisinengiso eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 7.26. Dute. 17.1.\x*.
\v 26 Njalo ungasingenisi isinengiso endlini yakho, hlezi ube yinto eqalekisiweyo njengaso; usenyanye lokusenyanya, unengwe lokunengwa yiso, ngoba siyinto eqalekisiweyo\x + Levi 27.28. Dute. 13.17. Josh. 6.17,18. 7.1. Mika 4.13.\x*.